description:
Parkour Jump Adventure Simulator is a fast-paced third-person platformer, the goal of the game is to jump over obstacles and buildings. Here you have an unlimited number of times you can jump for each level. 
      Jumps has 9 different levels (maps) in each map there are 6 simple levels and the last 7th level is a full stage, if you pass the full stage it allows you to play on the next map. Each world introduces exciting new gameplay mechanics for you to understand and master.
     More obstacles, more amazing parkour and jump tricks to perform, and more thrill guaranteed! With this parkour extreme and freerunning you have a chance to become best parkour master. It is one of the best parkour running games!
name: Parkour Jump Adventure - Simulator Stunt Tycoon Escape Kid Super Hero World Games
